{
  "content": "<h1 id=\"awaiteddom--documentorshadowroot\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#awaiteddom--documentorshadowroot\">#</a><a href=\"/docs/hero/basic-client/awaited-dom\">AwaitedDOM</a> <span>/</span> DocumentOrShadowRoot</h1>\n<div class='overview'><span class=\"seoSummary\">The <strong><code>DocumentOrShadowRoot</code></strong> mixin of the&nbsp;Shadow DOM API provides APIs that are shared between documents and shadow roots. The following features are included in both <code>Document</code> and <code>ShadowRoot</code>. </span></div>\n<h2 id=\"properties\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#properties\">#</a>Properties</h2>\n<h3 id=\"activeElement\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#activeElement\">#</a>.activeElement <div class=\"specs\"><i>W3C</i></div></h3>\n<p>Returns the <code>Element</code> within the shadow tree that has focus.</p>\n<h4 id=\"type-superelement\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#type-superelement\">#</a><strong>Type</strong>: <a href=\"/docs/hero/awaited-dom/super-element\"><code>SuperElement</code></a></h4>\n<h3 id=\"fullscreenElement\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#fullscreenElement\">#</a>.fullscreenElement <div class=\"specs\"><i>W3C</i></div></h3>\n<p>Returns the <code>Element</code> that's currently in full screen mode for this document.</p>\n<h4 id=\"type-superelement-1\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#type-superelement-1\">#</a><strong>Type</strong>: <a href=\"/docs/hero/awaited-dom/super-element\"><code>SuperElement</code></a></h4>\n<h3 id=\"pointerLockElement\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#pointerLockElement\">#</a>.pointerLockElement <div class=\"specs\"><i>W3C</i></div></h3>\n<p>Returns the element set as the target for mouse events while the pointer is locked. It returnsÂ <code>null</code> if lock is pending, the pointer is unlocked, or if the target is in another document.</p>\n<h4 id=\"type-superelement-2\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#type-superelement-2\">#</a><strong>Type</strong>: <a href=\"/docs/hero/awaited-dom/super-element\"><code>SuperElement</code></a></h4>\n<h2 id=\"methods\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#methods\">#</a>Methods</h2>\n<h3 id=\"caretPositionFromPoint\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#caretPositionFromPoint\">#</a>.caretPositionFromPoint <em>(x, y)</em> <div class=\"specs\"><i>W3C</i></div></h3>\n<p>Returns a <code>CaretPosition</code> object containing the DOM node containing the caret, and caret's character offset within that node.</p>\n<h4 id=\"arguments\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#arguments\">#</a><strong>Arguments</strong>:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>x <code>number</code>. The horizontal coordinate of a point.</li>\n<li>y <code>number</code>. The vertical coordinate of a point.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"returns-caretposition\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#returns-caretposition\">#</a><strong>Returns</strong>: <a href=\"/docs/hero/awaited-dom/caret-position\"><code>CaretPosition</code></a></h4>\n<h3 id=\"elementFromPoint\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#elementFromPoint\">#</a>.elementFromPoint <em>(x, y)</em> <div class=\"specs\"><i>W3C</i></div></h3>\n<p>Returns the topmost element at the specified coordinates.</p>\n<h4 id=\"arguments-1\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#arguments-1\">#</a><strong>Arguments</strong>:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>x <code>number</code>. The horizontal coordinate of a point, relative to the left edge of the current viewport.</li>\n<li>y <code>number</code>. The vertical coordinate of a point, relative to the top edge of the current viewport.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"returns-superelement\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#returns-superelement\">#</a><strong>Returns</strong>: <a href=\"/docs/hero/awaited-dom/super-element\"><code>SuperElement</code></a></h4>\n<h3 id=\"getSelection\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#getSelection\">#</a>.getSelection <em>()</em> <div class=\"specs\"><i>W3C</i></div></h3>\n<p>Returns a <code>Selection</code> object representing the range of text selected by the user, or the current position of the caret.</p>\n<h4 id=\"returns-selection\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#returns-selection\">#</a><strong>Returns</strong>: <a href=\"/docs/hero/awaited-dom/selection\"><code>Selection</code></a></h4>\n<h2 id=\"unimplemented-specs\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#unimplemented-specs\">#</a>Unimplemented Specs</h2>\n<h4 id=\"methods-1\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#methods-1\">#</a>Methods</h4>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th></th>\n<th></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code>elementsFromPoint()</code></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
